sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Cron
  participant Q as Queue
  participant H as Harness
  participant S as Session
  participant N as Notify

  C->>Q: create job with idempotency key
  Q->>S: append automation.triggered
  Q->>H: worker claims job
  H->>S: append job.started
  H->>H: resume or create session
  H-->>N: approval / progress / final notification
  H->>S: append job.completed or job.paused
